# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Rocket Racing — Streamed Maps · what git does NOT track
#  The pak binaries are distributed via GitHub Releases, never committed:
#   • a single .ucas is 60–165 MB — past GitHub's 100 MB hard per-file limit
#   • ~5.5 GB total across 57 plugins would make the repo miserable to clone
#  The repo keeps only docs, catalog data, scripts, and build provenance.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Full-game container set (~115 GB) — not part of this repo at all
/Paks/

# Per-map pak bundles under GFP/ — shipped as Release assets, not git
GFP/**/*.pak
GFP/**/*.sig
GFP/**/*.ucas
GFP/**/*.utoc
GFP/**/*.o.ucas
GFP/**/*.o.utoc
GFP/**/*.uondemandtoc
GFP/**/ManifestArchive.journal

# Release zips built locally by scripts/package_releases.ps1
/dist/

# Generated intermediate (the catalog is embedded in README.md)
CATALOG_BODY.md

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
